headline: Qnity to Preview New Brand and Product Launches at SEMICON West 2025
summary: Qnity, DuPont's Electronics business, today announced that it will be exhibiting at SEMICON West, Oct. 7-9, in Phoenix, Ariz. Following DuPont's intended spin-off of its electronics business targeted for Nov. 1, 2025*, Qnity Electronics, Inc. ("Qnity") is expected to be one of the largest and broadest publicly traded, global solutions providers for the semiconductor value chain. headline: DOW Launches Polymer Processing Aid Solution for Safer Packaging
summary: Dow unveils DOWSIL 5-1050, a safer, fluoropolymer-free solution for high-quality packaging films with regulatory compliance.
